": {"text": "3 月 3 日（报道），山东烟台南山公园动物园现「投喂是最虚伪的爱」「爱吃你自己吃」 等硬核禁止投喂标语，引发网友热议。园方表示，标语系 2025 年底借鉴其他动物园设置，对遏制乱投喂有一定效果。不过，标语获得关注后，园方已经暂时撤下了「投喂是最虚伪的爱」「爱吃你自己吃」两条标语，「有点犀利，而且新鲜感降低，劝阻的效果也会降低，后续会集思广益，设置更加合适的标语」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-80ca052f2198a85edf43eb072080529c.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "60 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2012548485900154728"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIiLmWlJS1yZh4EAMaCTExODYzMDMyMCC2u5/NBjAAOPMBQBVyEzIwMTI1NDg0ODU5MDAxNTQ3Mjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1772897055.883259", "card_id": "Q_2013309178861615075", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高一学生，应该熬夜学习吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c8c1096ecf955671f5b6bb1eae990f82_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2013309178861615075"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIiLmWlJS1yZh4EAMaCTExODY1Njc4OCCpxKrNBjAAODlAFnITMjAxMzMwOTE3ODg2MTYxNTA3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1772897055.883485", "card_id": "Q_664714735", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1041}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你享受一个人的独处时间吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "以前觉得我一定要拥有好多朋友，去哪里都和朋友一起，可现在我特别喜欢一个人，想做什么就做什么，没有孤独感反而很享受"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-116d44c9eaba774cfb08d707c1ce782a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664714735"}}, "at